      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under version control with documented test suite results demonstrating correct implementation of governing equations.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 was used under institutional license with version-controlled case files. Solver verification test suite results for incompressible Navier-Stokes and scalar transport were reviewed and confirmed passing. All simulation scripts and boundary condition files are archived in the project repository with checksums."
