      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry with bovine blood analog at physiological hematocrit. Operating conditions span the intended clinical range. The validation dataset is therefore directly representative of the COU, supporting the credibility of simulation results for regulatory decision-making."
