      "acceptanceCriteria": "The selected turbulence model and hemolysis power-law formulation must be justified for the Reynolds number range and flow regime present in the CPB pump.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on its validated performance for rotating machinery flows at Re 10^4–10^5. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was applied with published constants. Model form choices are consistent with peer-reviewed practice for CFD hemolysis prediction in blood pumps."
