    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate fidelity for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. NIH predictions agree with experimental data within 8.3% relative error, and all RH values satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Six factors were not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018. The credibility assessment supports regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device.",
